dct_title_s: Monroe Township, Middlesex County, New Jersey zoning 1968
dct_description_sm: Zoning map of Monroe Township in Middlesex County, New Jersey created in 1968 by William M. Rimmey, Township Engineer, 1380 Hamilton St., Somerset N.J. There is a hand written notation indicating revisions on Oct. 1, 1969 and 1970. Map is shaded by residential, business and industrial and rural zones.
